Complete Enhancement Summary: v1.0 → v2.0
Sitemap System (rewritten)
XSL stylesheet at /sitemap-xsl.xsl -- sitemaps are now human-readable with a styled table
Automatic pagination -- sites with >2,500 URLs split into sitemap-posts-2.xml, etc.
Google News sitemap (/sitemap-news.xml) -- 48-hour window, publication name, language, keywords
Video sitemap (/sitemap-video.xml) -- thumbnail, duration, player/content URLs
Author sitemap (/sitemap-authors.xml)
Per-language sitemaps -- optional /sitemap-en-posts.xml, /sitemap-fr-pages.xml
Database-sourced lastmod -- queries MAX(post_modified_gmt) instead of current timestamp
IndexNow protocol -- instant indexing for Bing, Yandex, Seznam, Naver
Deferred ping batching -- 30-second debounce for rapid publishes
noindex exclusion via meta_query at DB level, same-domain image filtering
Disables WordPress 5.5+ core sitemaps to prevent conflicts
Proper application/xml content type + cache headers
Schema / Structured Data (GEO-optimized)
SearchAction for Google sitelinks search box
SpeakableSpecification for voice search / AI assistants
SiteNavigationElement from primary menu
FAQPage auto-detection (Yoast blocks, heading+paragraph patterns, custom meta)
HowTo schema from post meta
Full Author entity with avatar, URL, sameAs profiles, linked via @id
Article enrichments: wordCount, articleSection, keywords, inLanguage, configurable type
WebPage: description, dates, primaryImageOfPage, speakable
Organization: contactPoint, 7 social platforms, image linking
Local Business: structured PostalAddress, GeoCoordinates, priceRange, openingHours as array
Product: WooCommerce Offers integration
Robots & Indexing
Professional auto-generated robots.txt with tracking param blocks, admin blocks
AI crawler management: block 14+ AI bots or write custom per-bot rules
Advanced meta robots: max-snippet, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview
Per-bot meta directives: separate googlebot and bingbot tags
Paginated noindex option
Site verification tags: Google, Bing, Yandex, Pinterest
IndexNow key file auto-served at /{key}.txt
Open Graph
og:image:width, og:image:height, og:image:type, og:image:alt
og:locale:alternate for multilingual
article:section, article:tag, article:author
og:video support, og:type=product and og:type=profile
Hreflang
Post type archive hreflang support
Author page hreflang support
Skips noindex and unpublished translations
Configurable x-default strategy
Admin & Cleanup
Updated all 7 settings pages with new features
Debug information panel in Tools
Version display in header
Removed 3 orphan duplicate files
Self-contained admin header (no root dependency)
7 social profile fields (added YouTube, Instagram, Pinterest, TikTok)